WEBVTT

00:03:28.427 --> 00:03:30.400
viringisha juu, viringika chini.

00:03:30.400 --> 00:03:32.803
Ni kidogo kama kua na sifa.

00:03:32.803 --> 00:03:34.298
Unapopata mchoro wa elektroniki,

00:03:34.298 --> 00:03:37.166
utakua unaviringika juu na chini kwa
mda mrefu,

00:03:37.166 --> 00:03:39.474
hivyo unapopitia haya mambo,

00:03:39.474 --> 00:03:42.559
kua tu mwangalifu unachoweka.

00:03:42.559 --> 00:03:45.938
Dhana namba mbili: Orpheus, mtu mzuri,

00:03:45.938 --> 00:03:49.666
anavutia kua nae, mzuri kwenye sherehe,
mwimbaji mzuri,

00:03:49.666 --> 00:03:52.883
kapoteza mpendwa wake, anajibahatishia
njia ya kuzimu

00:03:52.883 --> 00:03:55.490
mtu pekee kujibahatisha njia ya kuzimu,

00:03:55.490 --> 00:03:57.835
akavutia miungu ya kuzimu,

00:03:57.835 --> 00:04:00.730
wamuachie mrembo wake na sharti